254
00:18:17,340 --> 00:18:19,131
I admit I was angry that day,

255
00:18:19,147 --> 00:18:23,862
but no matter what, I've always loved you
more than the stars in the sky, and I still do.

256
00:18:24,231 --> 00:18:27,636
Really? You've always loved me, no matter what I did?

257
00:18:27,866 --> 00:18:29,464
Yes, of course I have.

258
00:18:30,226 --> 00:18:32,450
And does that feeling hold true to this day?

259
00:18:32,929 --> 00:18:35,192
I will always love you, no matter what,

260
00:18:35,273 --> 00:18:37,924
and I can clearly see now that you're the real Sherry.

261
00:18:38,266 --> 00:18:41,166
You have no idea how much I've missed you, little sister.

262
00:18:42,438 --> 00:18:43,318
I see.

263
00:18:44,610 --> 00:18:47,214
I feel the same, big brother.

264
00:18:47,461 --> 00:18:49,496
Sherry, please look this way.

265
00:18:49,512 --> 00:18:52,148
I'm begging you to show me that beautiful face of yours.

266
00:18:54,871 --> 00:18:56,484
Why are you crying, Sherry?

267
00:18:56,717 --> 00:18:57,936
Are you still sad?

268
00:18:58,347 --> 00:19:00,904
